metadata.name: I am Je$$yFries
metadata.description:
This artwork was created for the exhibition "I am..." powered by Gxrls Revolution and Jean-Michel Pailhon.

2023, I am Je$$yFries, hand-made watercolour painting blended with girly images via Midjourney AI.

Who am I? 
I am Je$$yFries, I am a fictional girly girl, I am your Bestie, I am an Internet Girly.

I love pink, Britney, Fries and cotton candy. 
I believe in Fries and Fries make me so happy!

Cause the only thing that a Girly needs is a Designer bag full of crunchy Fries.

Love you but not more than Fries.

XOXO,
Je$$yFries
